{"id": "art-241", "label": "Art. 241", "title": "Art. 241", "slug": "art-241", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 241 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1671814466\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1836\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1671814466\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>Administratorii <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\ncare urmeaz&#259; a participa la fuziune sau la divizare vor întocmi un proiect\nde fuziune sau de divizare, care va cuprinde:</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1312021897\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1835\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1312021897\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)forma, denumirea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> sediul\nsocial ale tuturor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> implicate\nîn fuziune sau divizare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1312778999\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1834\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1312778999\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)fundamentarea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> fuziunii sau ale diviz&#259;rii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_92285647\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1833\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_92285647\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)<span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span> aloc&#259;rii\nde <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> la societatea absorbant&#259; sau la <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> beneficiare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1943232915\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1832\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1943232915\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)data de la care <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunile</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ile</span> sociale prev&#259;zute la lit.\nc) dau <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span> dreptul de a participa\nla beneficii <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> orice <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;ii</span>\nspeciale care afecteaz&#259; acest drept;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_10244690\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1831\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_10244690\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)rata de schimb a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span> sociale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncuantumul eventualelor <span class=SpellE>pl&#259;&#355;i</span> în numerar;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_904292570\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1830\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_904292570\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)cuantumul primei de fuziune sau de divizare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1414697985\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1829\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1414697985\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)drepturile conferite de c&#259;tre societatea\nabsorbant&#259; sau beneficiar&#259; <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in&#259;torilor</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> care confer&#259; drepturi speciale <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> celor care <span class=SpellE>de&#355;in</span>\nalte valori mobiliare în afar&#259; de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>\nsau m&#259;surile propuse în <span class=SpellE>privin&#355;a</span> acestora;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_362713697\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1828\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_362713697\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)orice avantaj special acordat <span class=SpellE>exper&#355;ilor</span>\nla care se face referire la art. 243<sup>3</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nmembrilor organelor administrative sau de control ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span>\nimplicate în fuziune sau în divizare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_477812723\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1827\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_477812723\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)data <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;iilor</span>\nfinanciare ale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ilor</span> participante,\ncare au fost folosite pentru a se stabili <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\nfuziunii sau ale diviz&#259;rii;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1123773142\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1826\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1123773142\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>j)data de la care <span class=SpellE>tranzac&#355;iile</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbite sau divizate sunt\nconsiderate din punct de vedere contabil ca <span class=SpellE>apar&#355;inând</span>\n<span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> absorbante sau uneia ori alteia\ndintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> beneficiare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_354623519\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1825\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_354623519\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>k)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>în cazul\ndiviz&#259;rii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1402250360\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1824\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1402250360\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- descrierea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> repartizarea\nexact&#259; a activelor <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pasivelor care\nurmeaz&#259; a fi transferate fiec&#259;reia dintre <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1986187136\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1823\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1986187136\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>- repartizarea c&#259;tre <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarii</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ndivizate de <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>, respectiv <span\nclass=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;i</span> sociale, la <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nbeneficiare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> criteriul pe baza c&#259;ruia se\nface repartizarea.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}